">Sinh tra tử - Tình cảnh - 生查子－情景</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-Khoan/author-ryoCFWRVKVZLaDuFv6ToUg">Diêu Khoan</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Thi%C3%AAn-m%C3%A3-l%E1%BA%A1i/poem-lQAU5Us95qmKYdDBf6KapQ">Thiên mã lại - 天馬徠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Dung/T%C3%ACnh/poem-M3pT-SeHQrA1jQqQmxQiYg">Tình - 情</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Dung/author-qoi_3MEdeZkoj0TClsekFA">Ngô Dung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%90%C3%A0o/Uy%C3%AAn-%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BA%A3o/poem-5X1bHKkor57RayaeWl-Shg">Uyên ương thảo - 鴛鴦草</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%90%C3%A0o/author-YFc6G7OeOIRiUPVl88lFdA">Tiết Đào</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-II/poem-vDc-_oA-ETXOdzcBzyR_vg">Vô đề (II) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/author-Rv6locqJPIunovJpeqDNxA">Nguyễn Bỉnh Khiêm</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
